title: Simple Plan Made a Baywatch-Themed Video For 'I Don't Wanna Go to Bed'
text:
Simple Plan made a video for their song "I Don't Wanna Go to Bed" (featuring Nelly ) and it's more or less a gum commercial with just a few more boob shots than what a standard gum commercial would have. This is great. I bet a lot of people think this is great.
Maybe the theme of all this is "If it ain't broke, don't fix it, just take it to the beach. And then don't go to bed. Oh yeah, and boobs." Or something.
Before you watch, keep an eye out for these key moments:
- A random bomb going off on the beach. Why? Don't know.
- The lead singer bringing a drowning victim back to life by singing in her face.
- Weird crotch thrusts.
- David Hasselhoff is still wearing his Baywatch outfit. Why? And why is he wearing it while just sitting in his house watching TV?
